Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:34.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime has been abducted\Nby the Arrancars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:39.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save her,\NIchigo, Ishida, Sado, Rukia, and Renji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:42.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,have marched into Hueco Mundo,\Nthe world of the Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:46.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They crush the Arrancars\Nstanding in their way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:50.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and make their way to Las Noches,\NAizen's headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:52.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Guardian of the White Sand,\NRunuganga,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:57.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,drags them into the Forest of Menos\Ndeep beneath the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:04.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is separated from Ichigo and\Nthe others when they enter the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She meets a mysterious\NSoul Reaper named Ashido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:12.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, Ashido followed\NHollows into the Forest of Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He fought Hollows by himself\Nfor many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido… Why did\Nyou bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:31.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I talked, you'd respond,\Nask questions, and speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to let\Nmy friends hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia goes with Ashido to\Nlook for Ichigo and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:44.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But deep in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:50.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Adjuchas that control the forest\Nhad set a trap and were lying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we defeat him,\Nthe Menos will get slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:55.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:57.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire your Cero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim there, Gillians!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've brought a burden\Nwith you today, Ashido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should worry\Nmore about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:05.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido, you got hurt\Nbecause of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat that Adjuchas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:12.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two chatting about?!\NMaybe I should defeat you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:29.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodenoshirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Somenomai…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reconsider your thoughts…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,about whether I'm a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido… I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your friend's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:40.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido, it may not be\Nmy place to say this, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:45.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should return to\NSoul Society once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:49.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your feelings\Ntowards your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but the situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:54.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't like\Nthey were before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,More to the point, you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:02.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deceased friends will\Nforgive you if you leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I decide my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:13.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:21.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nel and the others'\NSpiritual Pressures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure they're here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:26.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We barge in and swipe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:35.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't waste time here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to start looking for\NRukia as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:43.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It's dangerous to barge in\Nwithout knowing the situation inside…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:55.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There were only traces\Nof their Spiritual Pressures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they were\Nmoved elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:13.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:32.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nel, you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:49.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:07.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to get you\Nwith one shot, but I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move a single hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:23.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, the Hollows\Nare going to eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you were\Nplanning to draw us out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by using them as bait\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:39.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who Lord Aizen placed\Nin charge of this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,says that he wants to\Nfight Ashido one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So we drew you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we made you come\Nto this amusing place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amusing place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:52.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this Spiritual Pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:02.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:04.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Where do you think\Nyou're going, Ashido?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ichigo!\N– Did they do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:40.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:42.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:47.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:51.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see our team play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:52.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dejected…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to\Nhold back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Reapers are\Nfighting over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:10.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to get\Nan understanding of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,their Spiritual Pressures\Nfrom here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't let you pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:24.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to sense\Nyour friends getting hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're going to die\Nbeing unable to do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You wretch…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish this already, Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought him many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Las Noches placed him\Nin charge of this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the others,\Nhe can't be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:45.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my final job in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido…you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:59.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, I want you to tell me\Nwhat's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:17.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ichigo! I'm scared!\N– That was so scary! Hold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They suddenly began\Nto move more slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend's Spiritual Pressure\Ndisappeared instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuginomai…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:28.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:36.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:50.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hihio Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we’ve\Ncleaned things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:20.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the exit is up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hollows told us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We can't leave\Nwithout Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NWe know where the exit is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:47.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, I'm glad that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:01.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Ashido…\NHe's a Soul Reaper like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:06.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved me and\Nallowed me to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Get here”?\NThe exit really is up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't believe us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:22.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! There's no hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!\NWe should thoroughly…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! They're still far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:31.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, our goal is to save Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido knows where the exit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:53.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get in from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't where you came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you pass through here,\Nget on the current of sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away, Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:24.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no… It's collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…\NDon't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:07.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your…friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:06.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! We got back to\Nthe surface alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:11.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that I'd live to see\Nthe gleaming moonlight ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:14.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore,\Nwe're almost at Las Noches!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:22.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– We did it! We did it!\N– We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:28.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido said that the Adjuchas' powers\Nchanged recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:35.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that fellow Soul Reapers\Njoined the Hollows
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:38.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and are trying to change the world\Nwith the Hogyoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:43.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashido had been fighting for\Nseveral hundreds of years
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under here as a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:57.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with saving Inoue,\Nlet's steal the Hogyoku from Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:24.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ashido, I'll come back for you.\NUntil then…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:43.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It unexpectedly suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:46.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:50.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now… Don't make a fuss\Nabout everything. It's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to inform you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:57.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends have\Nentered Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This wall…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:12.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to be\Nmade of Sekkiseki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:18.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not Sekkiseki, then we\Ncan break through by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:24.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't boss me around, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Why,” you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no other reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:21.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:22.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:26.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These clothes fit me perfectly.\NI was wondering how you knew my size.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:29.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is as Lord Aizen\Nhas intended it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:32.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He knew just by looking at me?!\NThat's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:34.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, that's not what you're\Nsupposed to be surprised about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:36.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:42.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi, what should we do\Nif our Zanpakuto breaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:43.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did yours break?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:45.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just theoretical.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:48.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could fix it for a fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Kurotsuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:53.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, here's a catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:57.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru is a monkey,\Nso option four is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:23:59.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:00.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ZABIMARU
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:05.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,PRODUCT CATALOG
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:02.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change their sex?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:04.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do this for me!